Track Pricing Data Using Event Log Files

To get a complete overview of your pricing procedures being executed, use the new Pricing events. Use the Pricing event log file type to measure how long it takes to run the pricing APIs. Use the event log files to track metrics related to pricing status, the error codes generated, and the pricing procedure configured and used.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions where Event Monitoring and Salesforce Pricing is enabled.
